---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="SocialProof for Lactation Consultants — Testimonials That Book New Parents | SocialProof"
  description="Collect and display authentic client testimonials for your lactation consulting practice. Let breastfeeding success stories build trust and book consultations. Free to start."
>
  <main class="for-page">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="eyebrow">For Lactation Consultants</p>
        <h1>You help new moms through their hardest moments — let them tell that story</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">When breastfeeding is working, the relief and gratitude parents feel is enormous. SocialProof captures those success stories and displays them where overwhelmed new parents can find you before they give up.</p>
        <div class="cta-group">
          <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn btn-primary">Start free — no credit card</a>
          <a href="/docs/quickstart" class="btn btn-secondary">See how it works</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pain">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Why lactation consultants struggle to show their impact</h2>
        <div class="pain-grid">
          <div class="pain-card">
            <h3>😤 Success happens off the record</h3>
            <p>A mom texts you "IT'S WORKING!" at 3am. That message is everything — but it's in your inbox, not on your website where the next struggling mom can see it.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pain-card">
            <h3>📸 New parent life is a blur</h3>
            <p>Even the most grateful clients are too sleep-deprived to write a Google review. You helped them through a crisis; they haven't forgotten you, they're just exhausted.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pain-card">
            <h3>🔗 High-urgency, high-doubt decision</h3>
            <p>Parents searching for a lactation consultant are often at their breaking point. They need to see that someone just like them solved this exact problem with your help.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="solution">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>SocialProof fixes this in 3 steps</h2>
        <ol class="steps">
          <li>
            <strong>Send a collect link</strong>
            <p>One week after a successful session, send a simple text: "Would you share how things are going in 2 minutes?" That's all it takes. A link, not a form, not a review site.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Approve with one click</strong>
            <p>Review submissions and approve the ones that tell the real story — "I was ready to quit and she saved our breastfeeding journey."</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Embed on your site</strong>
            <p>One script tag on your services page. Works with any website builder you use — Squarespace, Wix, WordPress, Jane App.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Built for Lactation Consultants</h2>
        <div class="feature-grid">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>⭐ Star ratings + text</h3>
            <p>Capture the story, not just the rating. The detail of a parent's journey — from pain and frustration to success — is what converts other parents into clients.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>📷 Client photos (optional)</h3>
            <p>Some parents are happy to share a photo. Others prefer privacy. Both are fine — you control what appears on your widget.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>🎨 Warm, professional design</h3>
            <p>Customize colors and fonts to match your practice aesthetic. Reassuring and professional, not clinical.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>📱 60-second mobile form</h3>
            <p>Parents fill it on their phone with one hand while the baby sleeps. Short enough to actually get completed.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>🔒 Privacy by default</h3>
            <p>Clients control how much they share. First name only, no photo — all valid. You approve everything before it goes live.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>🆓 Free forever tier</h3>
            <p>1 active widget, unlimited collections. Free forever for 1 active widget. No credit card to start.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pricing-cta">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Start collecting testimonials today</h2>
        <p>Free forever for 1 active widget. Pro is $9/mo for unlimited everything.</p>
        <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Get started free</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>
